The function should return [0.5, 0.5, 0.5], since all bins can fit the item and have the same remaining space.

Example 2:
For bins = [5, 5, 5], item = 6:
The function should return [0, 0, 0], since none of the bins can fit the item.

Example 3:
For bins = [10, 5, 8], item = 5:
The function should return [0.5, 1, 0.6], assuming some heuristic.

