### Solution Code:

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.log(item) * np.sin(bins) + np.cos(item) * bins
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item * np.log(bins)) + (item * np.log(bins)) + np.log(item)
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.log(item) * (item - bins) + np.log(item) * (item + bins)
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.log(bins) * (item - bins) + np.log(item) * (item + bins)
