```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item - np.mean(bins)) * np.cos(item + bins) + np.tan(np.pi * (item / bins))
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.log1p(item) * np.hypot(item, bins) + np.log2(np.mean(bins))
```

