- Array operations: mean, sum, product, etc.
- Hyperbolic functions: sinh, cosh, tanh.
- Random operations: random, choice, etc.
- Comparisons: <, >, <=, >=, ==, !=, and, or, etc.
- Logical operations: any, all, etc.
- Accessing array elements: itemgetter, etc.
- Custom functions: You can define any function, but it must be used in the priority function.

