### How to compute the priority:
The priority can be computed using various methods, such as:
- The remaining space in the bin (smallest remaining bin heuristic)
- The ratio of remaining space to the bin size (most empty heuristic)
- The difference between bin size and the item size (fitting factor)
- The sum of some function of the remaining space and the item size.

